.Dd February 22, 2001
.Dt QUOTA.USER 5
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm quota.user , quota.group
.Nd per file system quota database
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Each file system with active quotas should contain a
.Pa quota.user
and
.Pa quota.group
file in the file system root.
These files are created by
.Xr quotacheck 8 ,
and should be edited with
.Xr edquota 8 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr quota 1 ,
.Xr fstab 5 ,
.Xr edquota 8 ,
.Xr quotacheck 8 ,
.Xr quotaoff 8 ,
.Xr quotaon 8 ,
.Xr repquota 8
